    {
      "author": "Dian Arumningtyas",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107367157779481841554?hl=id",
      "rating": 3,
      "text": "Good coffee and (agreed with Julian Abraham's review) there's a good restaurant next door. Place is quite small, most of the seat were not cushioned.. might be a problem if you can't sit still with wooden chair (like me, it hurt my back after a while). I don't remember if they provide wifi here... Some tables were too small so it's kinda hard if you want to work on laptop, have a cup of coffee, have some papers or notebook laying on the table bcs there's not that much space. Oh they dont have snacks and you can smoke/vape in the room.\n\nAlso! They accept cash only. No debit or credit cards.",
      "textTranslated": "Kopinya enak dan (setuju dengan ulasan Julian Abraham) ada restoran bagus di sebelahnya. Tempatnya agak kecil, sebagian besar kursinya tidak empuk... mungkin akan menjadi masalah jika Anda tidak bisa duduk diam di kursi kayu (seperti saya, punggung saya sakit setelah beberapa saat). Saya tidak ingat apakah mereka menyediakan wifi di sini... Beberapa meja terlalu kecil sehingga agak sulit jika Anda ingin bekerja menggunakan laptop, minum kopi, atau meletakkan beberapa kertas atau buku catatan di atas meja karena tidak banyak ruang. Oh, mereka tidak menyediakan makanan ringan dan Anda boleh merokok/vape di dalam ruangan.\n\nJuga! Mereka hanya menerima uang tunai. Tidak menerima kartu debit atau kredit.",
      "date": "2017-04-12T15:21:06.839Z",
      "relativeDate": "9 tahun lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "responseFromOwner": null,
      "reviewId": "ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNnMjg2V0FnEAE",
